text:
="preserve">Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai is the longest running and Most Awarded Serial of Indian Television that airs on Star Plus
The series has been dubbes into vietnam as Bí mật của trái tim on THVL1 where it began to air in 2017.
The series has been dubbed into kazakhistan as келин бакыты on astana tv where it began to air in october 2017.
The series has been dubbed into bulgaria as закони на съдбата on diema family where it began to air in 2016
